      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "MUMMA EASY (6) is yet to miss the placings in an excellent record this track and trip which boasts five wins and two placings. Scored by 4 lengths last time (16.62) in a Restricted WIN H over 300m at this track. Makes strong appeal on best. CUMULATE (7) was strongly fancied latest and proved too good with a 1.75 lengths win at this track in a handy 16.69. Wide box to overcome but goes well over this trip. Winner at his latest appearance in one of the quickest times on the card. Bold showing expected again. ASTON ROCHELLE (8) doesn't win out of turn. Finished in the money last time though when second (16.86) at this track. Form at the trip sound including two wins. Remains without a win from the draw but has been in the placings two times from four attempts. Hard to beat again. Something for the Multiples: HE'S A COLLINDA (1)",
